OBJECTIVES
---------
**Primary**
- Recover valuable resources from storage halls
- Map safe passages through tunnel network
- Document Mirror Serpent behavior

**Secondary**
- Find Almir artifacts
- Restore water collection system
- Discover reason for settlement abandonment

RESOURCES
---------
• Abandoned Nomad supplies
• Functional water system
• Glass Grazer moss gardens
• Steel Vulture nesting materials

SPECIAL NOTES
------------
- Surface visibility varies with glass storms
- Tunnel stability decreases with depth
- Mirror Serpents more active during night
- Upper tunnels contain breathable air pockets
- Lower tunnels require breathing apparatus

*Would you like me to detail any specific aspect of this crystalline labyrinth further?*
